org.mitre.mat.core
Class IntAttributeType

java.lang.Object
  org.mitre.mat.core.AttributeType
      org.mitre.mat.core.IntAttributeType

public class IntAttributeType
extends AttributeType

The class that represents an integer-valued attribute. This attribute may optionally have either or both of a minimum and/or maximum allowable value specified. Alternately, it may optionally provide a fixed list of choices to select among. It is an error for both restrictions to be provided. An optional default value may be provided, or the value may default to the contents of the annotated span of text. If the latter, the value will be set to null if the text span cannot be coerced to an integer.
